::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-fold="true" code-summary="Show the code"}
gt(glance(fitModel) |>
     dplyr::select(r.squared, AIC, BIC)) |>
  fmt_number(decimals = 2) |>
  data_color(
    columns = c(r.squared),
    palette = "red")
```

